      }
    ],
    "statement": "Provenance shall support short-lived, scoped API key minting and revocation compatible with noscope's provider contract, enabling agents on networked machines to poll for ready tasks, claim work atomically, execute with scoped credentials, and post results back without a central dispatcher",
